> **Why this document exists.** The review pen-tests the live endpoint and
> requires a clear statement of **what data the exposed tools touch and how
> sensitive it is.** This document enumerates the data categories the tools
> access, classifies each, and states the two facts a reviewer most needs:
> (1) the read floor returns only the authorized caller's visible scope, and
> (2) whether any regulated data class (payment-card / health) is handled.

> **Honesty convention.** {{HONESTY_CONVENTION}}
